java.lang.Comparable
public class NakedTextNode
extends Node

This class represents text that is not exclusively contained by a single tag. Such text is referred to as "naked text" in this package. This object will occur in narrative-centric XML documents.

Author:
Frank Font (mrfont@room4me.com)
See Also:
Node, SmallXMLParser
